Global Injection And Infusion based Drug Delivery Devices Market Insights
Injection And Infusion based Drug Delivery Devices Market size was valued at USD 25.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 45.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Injection And Infusion based Drug Delivery Devices Market Overview
The global market for Injection and Infusion-based drug delivery devices has seen substantial growth in recent years, with an estimated market size valued at approximately USD 11.24 billion in 2023. This growth is primarily driven by the increasing demand for chronic disease management, technological advancements, and the growing preference for home care solutions. The market is poised to grow at a CAGR of 7.4% over the forecast period from 2023 to 2030, reaching an estimated value of USD 20.35 billion by 2030. The increasing adoption of biologics and the expanding geriatric population further fuel this growth, creating opportunities for manufacturers and healthcare providers in the market. Furthermore, technological innovations, such as connected devices and digital health platforms, are anticipated to shape the future of drug delivery solutions.

